org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model
Class SmsTask

java.lang.Object
  org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.BaseModel
      org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.SmsTask

public class SmsTask
extends BaseModel

A sms task that needs to be processed. For example: send message X to sakai group Y at time Z. When a sms task is processed, a record is inserted into SMS_MESSAGE for each message that must be sent out.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Julian Wyngaard
